sraeli\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When accepting this privileged appointment, sheurgedthe Israeli athletes to give inspiration and hope to their fellow citizens suffering from the tragedy.\", \"from\": 4582, \"to\": 4736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same IOC session, Cassy Wasserman, the chairperson of the 2028 Olympic Games in Los Angeles, also declared himself \\\"proud to be Jewish\\\" before his speech.\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4769, \"end\": 4778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999999998299245, \"rank\": 9.177380840345111e-11, \"text\": \"Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasserman_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 4825, \"end\": 4836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.920360113876301e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Olympic Games in Paris will take place amid conflict and contention.\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4927, \"end\": 4932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999991508142525, \"rank\": 8.491865439193464e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic truce and the neutrality of international sport is the idealism of the IOC.\", \"from\": 4979, \"to\": 5066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5062, \"end\": 5065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_C